description:
Osho_The Last Testament, Vol 1-16
The Future Is Always Open

Ma Prem Arup, DE RAJNEESH TIMES, AMSTERDAM,NETHERLANDS
First question

QUESTION: BHAGWAN, YOU ONCE SAID, "HOLLAND WILL BE ONE OF
MY MOST ORANGE COUNTRIES." WHY IS THAT SO?


ANSWER:
Holland is certainly going to be my country.
 My people are continuously growing in Holland.

You can see it already happening. It needs guts to be my red people, and Holland is one of the countries which has existed all through history with tremendous struggle, because the earth level is low and the sea level is higher.
